            Branding has undergone a significant transformation. What once relied on print media, business cards, and billboards has now shifted to digital platforms, where websites, social media, and online interactions shape a company’s identity. This digital shift has opened new opportunities for businesses, enabling them to reach wider audiences and engage customers in more dynamic ways. A well-structured <strong>branding package</strong> now plays a crucial role in maintaining consistency across these digital touchpoints, ensuring a cohesive brand identity. Whether you're launching a startup or refining an existing brand, understanding how branding has evolved is essential for staying relevant in today’s fast-paced market.
          </p>
