            <h3 class="fw-bold text-secondary mt-4">2. Interactive Websites: Turning Visitors into Customers</h3>
            <p class="w-100 lead">
              A website is often the first place people interact with your brand, so why not make it an experience? Interactive websites transform passive browsing into <strong>active engagement</strong>, keeping visitors interested for longer. Instead of scrolling through static text, users can explore your brand through interactive elements that respond to their clicks, scrolls, and swipes.
              <br /><br />
