              <br /><br />
              Some easy ways to make your branding more interactive include:
              <ul>
                <li>A logo that subtly moves or changes colors on your website.</li>
                <li>Loading animations that keep users entertained while pages load.</li>
                <li>Branded stickers and GIFs for social media.</li>
              </ul>
              These details may seem small, but they help build a brand identity that feels alive and engaging. 
            </p>
